<p><b>Tera</b> is a <a href="/wiki/Chadic_languages" title="Chadic languages">Chadic</a> language spoken in north-eastern <a href="/wiki/Nigeria" title="Nigeria">Nigeria</a> in the north and eastern parts of <a href="/wiki/Gombe_State" title="Gombe State">Gombe State</a> and <a href="/wiki/Borno_State" title="Borno State">Borno State</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-Harvcoltxt.7CTench.7C2007.7Cp.3D227_0-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Harvcoltxt.7CTench.7C2007.7Cp.3D227-0"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
<table id="toc" class="toc">
<tr>
